data.description: Newly Built Duplex located in Thatcher, Arizona, perfect for a first-time investor or owner occupant wanting extra income. Loan is assumable for an Owner Occupant. Units consist of 3 bedrooms/2 bathrooms and approximately 1,358 square feet EACH! One Unit is receiving $1,825 Per Month and the other unit is projected to receive $1,900 Per Month once leased. This property has very low repairs and maintenance. Tenants pay for their own electric bill and the owner only pays for the water bill. The Proforma CAP rate is 6.99%!
